Hi thanks for using this and btw sorry for my english XD
ok first unpack and copy the folder to your home it should be this way
"/home/you/conky/"
now open ~/conky/ and go to mpd folder and open sonata.sh and change " grep Artista " for what is in your language and also the line "Varios artistas-$ALBUM.png " for what it is needed an example
spanish  =   english
Artista   =   Artist
Varios artistas  =  Various Artist (I think xD  hope you get it )
and make it executable 
next copy the content in fonts to ~/.fonts and in a terminal run 
sudo fc-cache -fv 
for tint2 copy the tint2rc to ~/.confing/tint2/ replace if you want or make a backup of your 
previous skin 
and for last just make executable the file "start" and enjoy 

